Cell.Text: Malacath save me!
I don't think you'll be in any shape to fight when you get out of me. Hehehe.
Then I'll enjoy swallowing you again.
There's only one way out, and it ain't pretty.

Node.Caption: 000DevourmentPreyLethalAnger: Fuck you! When I get out of here...

Cell.Text: [S] G|Hah, that's a good one! Shout, then! Shout in my- | Oof! Ugh... Urk!
G|This again? The last three all said the same thing.

Node.Caption: 000DevourmentPreyLethalPersuade: I'm the Dovahkiin, Skyrim's last hope. If you digest me we'll all die.(Persuade)

Cell.Text: [S] G|Aaagh, damn you to Oblivion! That hurts!
G|Go ahead and try. My guts have handled worse than you.

Node.Caption: 000DevourmentPreyLethalIntimidate: I can still give you one hell of an ulcer from inside here. (Intimidate)

Cell.Text: [S] G|Thanks a lot my dear meal... | Give me that before I change my mind. | I'd be a rich person for every meal that pays for me to spare them.
G|Hah, you're not tricking me that easily.

Node.Caption: 000DevourmentPreyLethalBribe: You don't want to pick through your own shit for gold, do you?( gold)

Cell.Text: Oh, yes, I love it when they squirm helplessly...
Think you're special, huh? You're just food now.
Now why would I do that? You're a wonderfully filling meal.

Node.Caption: 000DevourmentPreyLethalBeg: Please, let me out! It can't end like this!

Cell.Text: G|Good! May the next blade find your heart.
G|Is... is that my end? Becoming some bastards ass fat?
G|I'm not a me-AAAAAGH! Help!

Node.Caption: 000DevourmentPredLethalTaunt2: Such a big meal. I doubt i will fit in my armor after this.

Cell.Text: G|Are you getting off on this, you sicko?
G|I hope an arrow hits you just before you come!
G|I'm not some sex toy! Let me out of here!
G|To Oblivion with you! I have some fight in me yet!
G|No... I... it can't end like this!
G|Aaagh, nooo... please...

Node.Caption: 000DevourmentPredLethalTaunt3: Squirm all you want... there's only one end for you.

Cell.Text: G|I'll be saying the same about you once I escape!
G|I'm a person, not a sweetroll!
G|Laugh it up while you can. Soon enough someone will say the same about you.

Node.Caption: 000DevourmentPredLethalTaunt5: If it's any consolation, you were delicious.

Cell.Text: G|You sadistic fuck, I hope you die the same way!
G|Not half as painful as what I'm going to do after I get out of here!
G|Please, no more... make it stop burning...
[S] Ohhhhhhh, yes, riiiiight there...
[S] Yes, yes, oh gods yes...
[S] Oh, oh, ohhh... ohhh...
Ah, I'm so glad you like it! Thought my tummy might smell a bit after that last bandit.
Stay as long as you like. Unlike the inns, I don't charge by the day.
Best way to survive a Skyrim winter, isn't it?
[S] G|Aww, very well. Let me know when you want to do this again.
[S] G|Already? Well, here goes...
G|Hmm... no, I think I'll keep you in there a little longer.
[S] G|Then we shall be together forever.

Node.Caption: 000DevourmentPreyNLDigestPlease: And you are dear to me. I want nothing more than to become part of you.

Cell.Text: What? No! You're far too dear to me...
[S] G|Really? Well, I'm not about about to pass up a free meal. | Besides, you'll add nicely to my ass...
[S] Ooh, naughty... how about this?
[S] I hope you don't mind if I do the same in here!
[S] G|I suppose Sovngarde calls to us all eventually... | Very well. I am yours, my friend.
Perhaps, but my time is not today.

Node.Caption: 000DevourmentPredNLDigestAskPersuade: We all die sooner or later. Wouldn't you rather die warm and embraced?(Persuade)

Cell.Text: [S] G|What, already?
[S] G|Thank you, I was low on air.
[S] G|We certainly must do this again sometime.

Node.Caption: 000DevourmentPredNLRelease: Hang on, I'm going to let you out...

Cell.Text: [S] G|Of course. I would love nothing more than to become part of your ass
[S] G|I though you would never ask... yes! I'm ready to go all the way.
[S] G|For a special person like you, I will gladly sacrifice my body and become part of you... You can digest me.
What? No! I have no such death wish.
So warm, so wet... I love it!
Ahh, wonderful... don't stop massaging me...
[S] G|Please... just make it quick.
I'm no fool! Digestion is digestion, regardless of your intent.

Node.Caption: 000DevourmentPredNLDigestAskIntimidate: We can do this two ways. One is much more painful. (Intimidate)

Cell.Text: [S] G|Thank you. Now I can go to Sovngarde with no regrets.
Are you out of your mind? No amount of gold can replace a lost life.

Node.Caption: 000DevourmentPredNLDigestAskBribe: I can make sure your loved ones are taken care of. ( gold)

Cell.Text: [S] G|What? No, why?!
[S] G|No, please! I thought this was just good fun!
[S] G|Ohh, I was hoping you'd say that...

Node.Caption: 000DevourmentPredNLDigestNice: Sorry, but I think I'm going to digest you now.

Cell.Text: [S] G|What?! No! You backstabbing piece of shit!
[S] G|You may have me at a disadvantage, but I'm not going down without a fight!
[S] G|By the gods, you'll pay for this treachery!

Node.Caption: 000DevourmentPredNLDigestForce: I can't believe you fell for that. Time to digest my lunch...

Cell.Text: I hope I'm filling enough for you.
Of all the stomachs I've been in, yours is my favorite.
Hello out there! I'm surprised you can hear me.
Aaaagh, it burns, it burns!
You... you bastard! Let me out, now!
No, not like this! I'm not food!
Mmmm, delicious... Oh! You needed something?
Yes? How are you doing in there?
You're surprisingly heavy, but I won't complain about carrying this burden.
Mmm, you're going to look so good added to my biceps and my butt...
Yes? Does my meal have something to say?
Shut up in there! I have a lot of digesting to do.
